
'''= services that match you with music you potentially like'''

See also the general treatment of [[Recommendation Engines]]


=Description=

Chris Dahlen has an extensive treatment of the history, present status and future of music recommendation projects here at http://www.pitchforkmedia.com/article/feature/36524-better-than-we-know-ourselves

It discusses [[Last FM]] and [[Pandora]]'s [[Music Genome Project]] in detail, then focuses on promising new projects such as [[Music IP]]


=Examples=

*[[Last FM]]: http://www.last.fm
*[[Pandora]]:  http://www.pandora.com
*[[Music IP]]:  http://musicip.com
*MusicStrands:  http://www.musicstrands.com
*Echo Nest:  http://www.echonest.com (see also Brian Whitman:  http://variogr.am and Tristan Jehan:  http://web.media.mit.edu/~tristan/)


